# Frontend Auto-Changelog

When you edit ANY file under `y_fi_frontend/`, automatically before your final response:

1. Prepend to `y_fi_frontend/.cursor/workflow/changelog.md` with timestamp `YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM (UTC+6)`
2. Update `api-integration.md` if API usage changed
3. Update `pages-and-routes.md` if routes/components changed

Do not wait for the user to say "update changelog". Mandatory on every code-changing turn.
